Philip John Boon



Philip John Boon was Born in July, 1959 (58 years old)  a resident of Innospec Manufacturing Park, Oil Sites Road, Ellesmere Port, Cheshire, CH65 4EY (United Kingdom) having British nationality and was first ever appointed as Director in Innospec Limited on Monday 29 March 2010 and as per the records from Registrar of Companies last appointment was in Innospec Environmental Limited as Director on Monday 13 February 2012 and currently holding positions as Director Philip John Boon was appointed in over 3 companies and currently holding positions in over 2 Companies.













