Insider Activity


Individual




Philip John Boon



Dr. Philip J. Boon is Chief Operating Officer at Innospec, Inc.
Dr. Boon was previously employed as Marketing Director by Octel Corp., Regional Director-EMEA by Innospec Active Chemicals Ltd., and Regional Director-EMEA by Innospec Fuel Specialties LLC.
He received his doctorate degree from the University of Leicester.



